"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-features-olympic-cross-country-day-paris-865448\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tomorrow is one of the biggest days in horse sport, one that only comes round every four (well, three on this occasion) years - it's Olympic cross-country day for the eventers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, if you are tuning into the action from theParis Gamesat home, what should you look out for?\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read on, we have got you covered\\u2026    1.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The beauty of thecross-country course.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre Le Goupil's track has been decorated to fit in with the French theme and particularlythe history of Versailles- you can admire fences such as the Enlightenment Bookcase and the Etoile Royal Waters.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\", \"score\": 0.9935874826063947, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Goupil\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\"}, {\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9955636928613295, \"rank\": 0.002680818719021509, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Age_of_Enlightenment\", \"score\": 0.9999694395966785, \"rank\": 3.035441935369651e-05, \"text\": \"Enlightenment\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Age_of_Enlightenment\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Age_of_Enlightenment\"}, {\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bookcase\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bookcase\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bookcase\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bookcase\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In terms of the actual challenge for riders, it'll be fascinating to see what happens at fence 10.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Named the Vauban Citadel, this complex offers a baffling array of options - there are four different fences riders can jump as element b and another four available as part c. It will probably prove to be one of those situations where riders hone in on two options and everyone takes one of those - or might we see a wide variety of approaches?\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brits.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Brits\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB holds both gold positions after the first phase, having set a new Olympic record team score in eventing dressage andLaura Collett(London 52) havingpunched in a new Olympic record mark individually.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9982466841113329, \"rank\": 0.0014276125922735648, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999808856048, \"rank\": 1.5106016913206187e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pressure is now on Laura,Ros Canter(Lordships Graffalo) andTom McEwen(JL Dublin) to retain those positions.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.7419393022469258, \"rank\": 0.33591804363048355, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\", \"score\": 0.9999916464361043, \"rank\": 8.353632659154385e-06, \"text\": \"McEwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\"}, {\"begin\": 1296, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999539113571, \"rank\": 4.6088717104476805e-08, \"text\": \"JL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9958308147741765, \"rank\": 0.004179714135385106, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3.Chris Burton.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burton_(equestrian)\", \"score\": 0.7515418114884803, \"rank\": 0.2975206611570445, \"text\": \"Chris Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burton_(equestrian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burton_(equestrian)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian has had nearly three years out of eventing after giving up the sport to go showjumping in 2021.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.242377673706548e-16, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He returned in the spring this year and goes into cross-country sharing the individual bronze position with China's Alex Hua Tian.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.984751410835042, \"rank\": 0.014941902997359775, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Hua_Tian\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Hua Tian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Hua_Tian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Hua_Tian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris used to be one of the fastest riders in the sport, so let us see if that's still true when he takes to the course with Shadow Man.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.716055052124075e-12, \"text\": \"Shadow Man\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which leads us on to\\u2026  4.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The optimum time.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The target is 9min 2sec and whether riders can make it will have a huge influence on the competition.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only will time-faults change the leaderboard, but if the time is tighter riders will have to take riskier lines and tackle all the direct routes and that will influence the competition.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"5.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressage trot-up.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, cross-country is the major player tomorrow, but at 7.40am local time (6.40am British time), the pure dressage horses will be presented for inspection to ensure they are fit to start their competition on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2172, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9980068066302737, \"rank\": 0.0011563739825222118, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might also be interested in:            Stay in touch with all the news in the run-up to and throughout the major shows and events during 2025 and beyond with a Horse & Hound subscription.Subscribe todayfor all you need to know ahead of these major events, plus online reports on the action as it happens from our\\u00a0expert team of reporters\\u00a0and in-depth analysis in our special commemorative magazines.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Houn